Greetings All,
Good news, a spell checker is now available for use on this and all
other groups!
Here's how. Download the Google tool bar from  . It's a
button on the tool bar that checks the spelling of any text box on a
web site that you write in. After you write in the message box for the
group, click the button and it'll highlight any mistakes. Then, you
click on the highlighted text and it'll give you correctly spelled
options to choose from.
The tool bar works in MS IE, FireFox and others.

